constitution.directive: Ship NXTG-Forge as a production-ready developer tool with proper licensing, deployment strategy, and governance visibility
vision: Ultimate Chief of Staff for Developers - AI-orchestrated productivity 10x
Production planning and legal compliance as first-class features (no one else does this)
100% transparency in all decisions and operations

workstreams.name: v3 Post-Launch Roadmap (Weeks 1-4)
workstreams.description: Complete 4-week roadmap: production polish, agent ecosystem, infrastructure, marketing

tasks.name: Week 1: Production Polish (any types, TODOs, tests)
Week 2: Agent Ecosystem (22 agents, CI/CD, Sentry, API docs)
Week 4: E2E Tests + Performance + Marketing + Beta + Docs

workstreams.name: Terminal UX Fixes
workstreams.description: Full-width viewport containment, panel layout, double header fix

tasks.name: Remove max-w-7xl container for terminal view
Fix double header (hide AppHeader on terminal)
Fix viewport overflow with flex min-h-0 chain
Expand panels to full browser width
Add Dashboard nav button to terminal header

workstreams.name: License & Monetization Decision
workstreams.description: MIT open source license. 58 packages audited, all permissive. LICENSE and SECURITY.md created.

workstreams.name: Deployment Medium Decision
workstreams.description: Claude Code Plugin (primary). Distributed as .claude/commands + .claude/agents + CLAUDE.md. Users install via git clone. Zero npm dependency.

workstreams.name: Governance HUD Data Pipeline
workstreams.description: Wire real data into governance HUD. Currently shows stale Jan 29 data. Need: auto-update from sessions, git state, test metrics, blocking decisions.

tasks.name: Wire session events to sentinel API
Add git state tracking to HUD

workstreams.name: Documentation Hygiene & Organization
workstreams.description: Root cleaned to 5 standard files (README, LICENSE, CLAUDE, CHANGELOG, CONTRIBUTING, SECURITY). 18 docs organized into subdirs. .claude/forge/ cleaned of stale config.

workstreams.name: Production Compliance Feature (Dog-food)
workstreams.description: Capture production planning + legal compliance as an nxtg-forge feature. Tech stack scanning, license checks, SBOM generation, deployment readiness.

workstreams.name: Multi-Framework Agent Adapter
workstreams.description: Abstract the agent orchestration layer so NXTG-Forge can drive Claude Code (native Agent Teams), OpenAI Codex CLI, and Google Gemini CLI through a unified adapter interface. Claude backend uses native Task/TeamCreate tools; Codex/Gemini backends use the existing AgentWorkerPool with framework-specific spawn commands.

tasks.name: Define AgentBackend adapter interface (spawn, status, message, shutdown)
Add backend auto-detection (detect installed CLI tools)
Update worker routes to use adapter interface
